{"id":226825,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":5,"day":20}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"174","ytitle":"","mtitle":"夏令防疫须知","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"(甲)六要:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)要快打霍乱预防针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)要喝煮开的水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)要在饮食品上加盖纱罩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)要把垃圾倒在垃圾箱里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(五)要扑灭苍蝇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(六)发现疑似霍乱病人，要赶快报告卫生防疫站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(乙)六不:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)不喝生水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)不吃剥皮洒生水的瓜果。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(三)不吃苍蝇爬过的东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(四)不吃不洁的冷饮食品。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(五)不随地大小便。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(六)不随地抛弃瓜皮果壳及垃圾。"}]}